WEBVTT

00:01.510 --> 00:04.530
So beautiful it was,

00:04.720 --> 00:10.500
that you all could come and give me such a surprise.

00:12.240 --> 00:16.320
Of course I love you very much, no doubt.

00:18.780 --> 00:24.400
My love is not mental, is not emotional,

00:25.560 --> 00:28.540
it’s existence itself.

00:29.580 --> 00:34.780
I exist with it. It’s my innate nature,

00:35.800 --> 00:41.020
which I could not enjoy unless and until it is reflected.

00:41.740 --> 00:43.760
It has to be reflected,

00:43.940 --> 00:47.540
and today I felt the reflection in you people.

00:47.720 --> 00:52.600
I was so overjoyed, so very overjoyed.

00:52.800 --> 00:57.220
Everything seems so beautiful.

00:58.080 --> 01:02.780
All these petty problems that trouble you,

01:02.980 --> 01:06.960
and sometimes try to bother Me also,

01:07.120 --> 01:09.440
just disappeared.

01:09.620 --> 01:13.740
You just felt that everybody is so cleansed and so beautiful,

01:13.920 --> 01:17.340
everybody’s ego washed off

01:17.540 --> 01:23.140
and the nectar of the beauty of love is just

01:23.320 --> 01:26.360
pouring into them.

01:27.980 --> 01:30.540
It’s not easy to describe,

01:30.740 --> 01:34.260
that was Nirananda, I felt it today,

01:34.440 --> 01:37.440
complete Nirananda.

01:37.980 --> 01:42.800
To feel Your own joy reflected is something so

01:43.340 --> 01:45.960
boundless that You cannot put them

01:46.160 --> 01:49.380
into the limitations of words.

01:50.140 --> 01:54.200
You have given me the greatest joy today

01:57.100 --> 02:01.760
and a very great feeling

02:01.940 --> 02:08.260
that Sahaja Yoga now will be established very well

02:08.440 --> 02:11.140
in Germany especially.

02:11.300 --> 02:14.620
I always felt about Germany

02:14.800 --> 02:18.000
that it needed a special help

02:18.180 --> 02:22.620
and the way you all have rushed here

02:22.800 --> 02:26.480
is something like a place,

02:26.660 --> 02:30.320
say, in the hand or in the feet, there is some pain,

02:30.500 --> 02:36.160
so all the attention moves towards that, like that.

02:36.700 --> 02:40.880
Germany is a very strong nation

02:41.200 --> 02:45.200
and if you could take them to Sahaja Yoga,

02:45.400 --> 02:48.700
we’ll have that metal within us. It’s very important.

02:48.880 --> 02:52.880
Every country has something special.

02:53.060 --> 02:56.540
The metal of Germany is very important

02:56.740 --> 03:01.440
and if that comes into us, we’ll have that courage.

03:02.940 --> 03:06.160
So may God bless you all for that.
